gw.api.domain.account

Interface PolicyCommissionHistoryEntry


  • public interface PolicyCommissionHistoryEntry
    Represents an entry in the history of producer codes occupying a role on a policy period.
    Author:
    pdalbora

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      java.util.Date getEndDate()
      Gets the date on which the PolicyCommission stopped being in this role on the policy period.
      PolicyCommission getPolicyCommission()
      Gets the PolicyCommission associated with this entry.
      java.util.Date getStartDate()
      Gets the date on which the PolicyCommission started in this role on the policy period.

    • Method Detail

      • getPolicyCommission

        PolicyCommission getPolicyCommission()
        Gets the PolicyCommission associated with this entry.
        Returns:
        the PolicyCommission, or null if this entry represents a time period in which no producer code existed in the role.

      • getStartDate

        java.util.Date getStartDate()
        Gets the date on which the PolicyCommission started in this role on the policy period.
        Returns:
        the start date, or null if this PolicyCommission represents the original producer code in the role.

      • getEndDate

        java.util.Date getEndDate()
        Gets the date on which the PolicyCommission stopped being in this role on the policy period.
        Returns:
        the end date, or null if this PolicyCommission is still the current producer code in the role.
